{{IPA|/z/}} occurs only in unassimilated [[loanword]]s.  {{IPA|/tʃ/}} and {{IPA|/dʒ/}} occur mainly in loanwords, but also in some dialects as developments from {{IPA|/tj/}} and {{IPA|/dj/}}; the [[voiceless consonant|voiceless]] [[nasal consonant|nasals]] {{IPA|/m̥/}}, {{IPA|/n̥/}}, {{IPA|/ŋ̊/}} occur only as a consequence of [[Welsh morphology#Initial consonant mutation|nasal mutation]].

