==Sentences==
To ask how much an item costs, say:
{{Hebrew-Vocab|?כַּמָּה זֶה עָלָה|How much does this cost?|question|''Kamah'' (KAH-mah) ''zeh oleh'' (OH-leh)?}}

A common shorthand is:
<div style="text-align:right"><font size=4>?כּמה זה</font></div>
''Kamah zeh''?  =  How much is this?

If you are pointing at a specific item, say a radio, you might say:
<div style="text-align:right"><font size=4>?כּמה הרדיוֹ</font></div>
''Kamah haradio'' (ha-RAH-dee-yo)?  = How much is the radio?

{{Hebrew-Large| ?מִי הִיא}} -- Who is she?

